INSERT OVERWRITE DIRECTORY '/tmp/TRANS_EXECUTION_GMMAPR'
ROW FORMAT DELIMITED FIELDS TERMINATED BY '|' STORED AS TEXTFILE
SELECT TABLA_APR,WF_NAME,WORKFLOW,SUM(
CASE ESTATUS_CRU
WHEN 'PENDIENTE' THEN 1
ELSE '0'
END) as faltante
FROM bddlorg.TRANS_EXECUTION_GMMAPR
GROUP BY TABLA_APR , WF_NAME,WORKFLOW
HAVING faltante=0

INSERT OVERWRITE DIRECTORY '/tmp/TRANS_EXECUTION_GMMAPR'
ROW FORMAT DELIMITED FIELDS TERMINATED BY '|' STORED AS TEXTFILE
SELECT TABLA_APR,WF_NAME,WORKFLOW,SUM(
CASE ESTATUS_CRU
WHEN 'PENDIENTE' THEN 1
ELSE '0'
END) as faltante
FROM bddlorg.TRANS_EXECUTION_GMMAPR
GROUP BY TABLA_APR , WF_NAME,WORKFLOW
HAVING faltante=0

UPDATE bddlorg.TRANS_EXECUTION_GMMAPR
SET ESTATUS_CRU= 'FINALIZADO',

select  cve_siniestro,cve_cobertura_tarificable,cve_cobertura_afecta, cob_contab, cob_contab2, val_cve_afectado         from (                 Select a.cve_siniestro, a.cve_cobertura_tarificable, a.cve_cobertura_afecta, a.cob_contab, b.cob_contab2,                 case when a.cob_contab = b.cob_contab2  then 'V'                  else 'F' end as val_cve_afectado                 from                         (select cve_siniestro,cve_cobertura_tarificable,cve_cobertura_afecta, MAX(cob_contab)  as cob_contab                         from  bddlapr.aut_siniestro_cob_afecta_271119                          where subconcepto_de_reserva = 'S' and cve_tipo_mov_siniestro = 'R'                         GROUP BY cve_siniestro,cve_cobertura_tarificable,cve_cobertura_afecta)A                 inner join                         (select cve_siniestro, cve_cobertura_tarificable, cve_cobertura_afecta, MAX(cob_contab)  as cob_contab2                         from bddldes.aut_siniestro_cob_afecta_insumo_nvos_261119                         GROUP BY cve_siniestro, cve_cobertura_tarificable, cve_cobertura_afecta                         )B                 on                         a.cve_siniestro  =   b.cve_siniestro and                         a.cve_cobertura_tarificable =   b.cve_cobertura_tarificable and                         a.cve_cobertura_afecta    =   b.cve_cobertura_afecta                      ) R where (cob_contab IS NOT NULL) AND cob_contab2 IS NOT NULL AND val_cve_afectado = 'F'

select  cve_siniestro,cve_cobertura_tarificable,cve_cobertura_afecta, fecomuni_fch, fecomuni_fch2, val_cve_afectado         from (                 Select a.cve_siniestro, a.cve_cobertura_tarificable, a.cve_cobertura_afecta, a.fecomuni_fch, b.fecomuni_fch2,                 case when a.fecomuni_fch = b.fecomuni_fch2  then 'V'                  else 'F' end as val_cve_afectado                 from                         (select cve_siniestro,cve_cobertura_tarificable,cve_cobertura_afecta, fecomuni_fch  as fecomuni_fch                         from  bddlapr.aut_siniestro_cob_afecta_271119                         where subconcepto_de_reserva = 'S' and cve_tipo_mov_siniestro = 'R')A                 inner join                         (select cve_siniestro, cve_cobertura_tarificable, cve_cobertura_afecta, fecomuni_fch  as fecomuni_fch2                         from bddldes.aut_siniestro_cob_afecta_insumo_nvos_261119                         GROUP BY cve_siniestro, cve_cobertura_tarificable, cve_cobertura_afecta, fecomuni_fch, fecomuni_fch2                         )B                 on                         a.cve_siniestro  =   b.cve_siniestro and                         a.cve_cobertura_tarificable =   b.cve_cobertura_tarificable and                         a.cve_cobertura_afecta    =   b.cve_cobertura_afecta                      ) R where (fecomuni_fch IS NOT NULL) AND fecomuni_fch2 IS NOT NULL AND val_cve_afectado = 'F'

select  cve_siniestro,cve_cobertura_tarificable,cve_cobertura_afecta, fecomuni_fch, fecomuni_fch2, val_cve_afectado         from (                 Select a.cve_siniestro, a.cve_cobertura_tarificable, a.cve_cobertura_afecta, a.fecomuni_fch, b.fecomuni_fch2,                 case when a.fecomuni_fch = b.fecomuni_fch2  then 'V'                  else 'F' end as val_cve_afectado                 from                         (select cve_siniestro,cve_cobertura_tarificable,cve_cobertura_afecta, fecomuni_fch  as fecomuni_fch                         from  bddlapr.aut_siniestro_cob_afecta_271119                         where subconcepto_de_reserva = 'S' and cve_tipo_mov_siniestro = 'R')A                 inner join                         (select cve_siniestro, cve_cobertura_tarificable, cve_cobertura_afecta, fecomuni_fch  as fecomuni_fch2                         from bddldes.aut_siniestro_cob_afecta_insumo_nvos_261119                         GROUP BY cve_siniestro, cve_cobertura_tarificable, cve_cobertura_afecta, fecomuni_fch, fecomuni_fch2                         )B                 on                         a.cve_siniestro  =   b.cve_siniestro and                         a.cve_cobertura_tarificable =   b.cve_cobertura_tarificable and                         a.cve_cobertura_afecta    =   b.cve_cobertura_afecta                      ) R where (fecomuni_fch IS NOT NULL) AND fecomuni_fch2 IS NOT NULL AND val_cve_afectado = 'F'

select  cve_siniestro,cve_cobertura_tarificable,cve_cobertura_afecta, fecomuni_fch, fecomuni_fch2, val_cve_afectado         from (                 Select a.cve_siniestro, a.cve_cobertura_tarificable, a.cve_cobertura_afecta, a.fecomuni_fch, b.fecomuni_fch2,                 case when a.fecomuni_fch = b.fecomuni_fch2  then 'V'                  else 'F' end as val_cve_afectado                 from                         (select cve_siniestro,cve_cobertura_tarificable,cve_cobertura_afecta, fecomuni_fch  as fecomuni_fch                         from  bddlapr.aut_siniestro_cob_afecta_271119                         where subconcepto_de_reserva = 'S' and cve_tipo_mov_siniestro = 'R')A                 inner join                         (select cve_siniestro, cve_cobertura_tarificable, cve_cobertura_afecta, fecomuni_fch  as fecomuni_fch2                         from bddldes.aut_siniestro_cob_afecta_insumo_nvos_261119                         GROUP BY cve_siniestro, cve_cobertura_tarificable, cve_cobertura_afecta, fecomuni_fch, fecomuni_fch2                         )B                 on                         a.cve_siniestro  =   b.cve_siniestro and                         a.cve_cobertura_tarificable =   b.cve_cobertura_tarificable and                         a.cve_cobertura_afecta    =   b.cve_cobertura_afecta                      ) R where (fecomuni_fch IS NOT NULL) AND fecomuni_fch2 IS NOT NULL AND val_cve_afectado = 'F'

CREATE TABLE MES_ANT AS
SELECT anio_mes_contable, num_reclamacion, num_solicitud_tramite, id_solicitud, 
CASE WHEN num_solicitud_tramite = -999 THEN id_solicitud ELSE CAST(num_solicitud_tramite AS string) END AS tramite_siniestro,
CASE WHEN ind_tramite_fondo_cashflow IN ("NULL","SL","") THEN "" ELSE "CF" END AS ind_tramite_fondo_cashflow,
cve_unidad_pago,
CASE 
WHEN cve_unidad_pago IN ('U002', 'U099', 'MXP')  THEN 'MXP' ELSE 'USD' END AS clasif_proveedor,
cve_modalidad, ramo, ramo_conjunto, cve_subconcepto_reserva, mto_importe_siniestral, mto_neto, 
num_poliza, num_poliza_cobranza, num_version_poliza, hosp_nom, hosp_gpo,
CASE 
WHEN hosp_nom = 'SOHIN' THEN 'Farm'
WHEN hosp_nom = 'ADM SALUD' THEN 'SAUX'
WHEN cve_subconcepto_reserva = 'HM' AND hosp_gpo = 'Grupo Star Medica' THEN 'HM' 
WHEN id_proveedor <> 0 AND hosp_tpo = 'Hosp' THEN 'Hosp'
WHEN id_proveedor <> 0 AND hosp_tpo = 'Hosp Extr' THEN 'Extranjero'
WHEN id_proveedor <> 0 AND hosp_tpo = 'Farmacias' THEN 'Extranjero'
WHEN cve_subconcepto_reserva IN ('RE','DH') AND cve_modalidad = 'RE' THEN 'RE'
WHEN id_proveedor = 0 OR hosp_tpo IN ('ND','Otro') OR hosp_tpo IS NULL AND cve_subconcepto_reserva = 'HM' THEN 'HM'
ELSE 'SAUX'
END AS TIPO_GASTO
FROM bddldes.tmp_gmm_siniestros_5
WHERE id_solicitud <> '0092051333' AND anio_mes_contable >= 201811 AND anio_mes_contable <= 201910

Operation Text: select  cve_siniestro,cve_cobertura_tarificable,cve_cobertura_afecta, fecomuni_fch, fecomuni_fch2, val_cve_afectado         from (                 Select a.cve_siniestro, a.cve_cobertura_tarificable, a.cve_cobertura_afecta, a.fecomuni_fch, b.fecomuni_fch2,                 case when a.fecomuni_fch = b.fecomuni_fch2  then 'V'                  else 'F' end as val_cve_afectado                 from                         (select cve_siniestro,cve_cobertura_tarificable,cve_cobertura_afecta, fecomuni_fch  as fecomuni_fch                         from  bddlapr.aut_siniestro_cob_afecta_271119                         where subconcepto_de_reserva = 'S' and cve_tipo_mov_siniestro = 'R')A                 left join                         (select cve_siniestro, cve_cobertura_tarificable, cve_cobertura_afecta, fecomuni_fch  as fecomuni_fch2                         from bddlapr.aut_siniestro_cob_afecta                         GROUP BY cve_siniestro, cve_cobertura_tarificable, cve_cobertura_afecta, fecomuni_fch, fecomuni_fch2)B                 on                         a.cve_siniestro  =   b.cve_siniestro and                         a.cve_cobertura_tarificable =   b.cve_cobertura_tarificable and                         a.cve_cobertura_afecta    =   b.cve_cobertura_afecta                      ) R where (fecomuni_fch IS NOT NULL) AND fecomuni_fch2 IS NOT NULL AND val_cve_afectado = 'F'

select  cve_siniestro,cve_cobertura_tarificable,cve_cobertura_afecta, desc_causa_siniestro, desc_causa_siniestro2, val_cve_afectado         from (                 Select a.cve_siniestro, a.cve_cobertura_tarificable, a.cve_cobertura_afecta, a.desc_causa_siniestro, b.desc_causa_siniestro2,                 case when a.desc_causa_siniestro = b.desc_causa_siniestro2  then 'V'                  else 'F' end as val_cve_afectado                 from                         (select cve_siniestro,cve_cobertura_tarificable,cve_cobertura_afecta, desc_causa_siniestro  as desc_causa_siniestro                         from  bddlapr.aut_siniestro_cob_afecta_271119                         where subconcepto_de_reserva = 'S' and cve_tipo_mov_siniestro = 'R')A                 left join                         (select cve_siniestro, cve_cobertura_tarificable, cve_cobertura_afecta, desc_causa_siniestro  as desc_causa_siniestro2                         from bddlapr.aut_siniestro_cob_afecta                         GROUP BY cve_siniestro, cve_cobertura_tarificable, cve_cobertura_afecta, desc_causa_siniestro, desc_causa_siniestro2)B                 on                         a.cve_siniestro  =   b.cve_siniestro and                         a.cve_cobertura_tarificable =   b.cve_cobertura_tarificable and                         a.cve_cobertura_afecta    =   b.cve_cobertura_afecta                      ) R where (desc_causa_siniestro IS NOT NULL) AND desc_causa_siniestro2 IS NOT NULL AND val_cve_afectado = 'F'

select  cve_siniestro,cve_cobertura_tarificable,cve_cobertura_afecta, cve_causa_siniestro, cve_causa_siniestro2, val_cve_afectado         from (                 Select a.cve_siniestro, a.cve_cobertura_tarificable, a.cve_cobertura_afecta, a.cve_causa_siniestro, b.cve_causa_siniestro2,                 case when a.cve_causa_siniestro = b.cve_causa_siniestro2  then 'V'                  else 'F' end as val_cve_afectado                 from                         (select cve_siniestro,cve_cobertura_tarificable,cve_cobertura_afecta, cve_causa_siniestro  as cve_causa_siniestro                         from  bddlapr.aut_siniestro_cob_afecta_271119                         where subconcepto_de_reserva = 'S' and cve_tipo_mov_siniestro = 'R')A                 left join                         (select cve_siniestro, cve_cobertura_tarificable, cve_cobertura_afecta, cve_causa_siniestro  as cve_causa_siniestro2                         from bddlapr.aut_siniestro_cob_afecta                         GROUP BY cve_siniestro, cve_cobertura_tarificable, cve_cobertura_afecta, cve_causa_siniestro, cve_causa_siniestro2)B                 on                         a.cve_siniestro  =   b.cve_siniestro and                         a.cve_cobertura_tarificable =   b.cve_cobertura_tarificable and                         a.cve_cobertura_afecta    =   b.cve_cobertura_afecta                      ) R where (cve_causa_siniestro IS NOT NULL) AND cve_causa_siniestro2 IS NOT NULL AND val_cve_afectado = 'F'

select  cve_siniestro,cve_cobertura_tarificable,cve_cobertura_afecta, cve_causa_siniestro, cve_causa_siniestro2, val_cve_afectado         from (                 Select a.cve_siniestro, a.cve_cobertura_tarificable, a.cve_cobertura_afecta, a.cve_causa_siniestro, b.cve_causa_siniestro2,                 case when a.cve_causa_siniestro = b.cve_causa_siniestro2  then 'V'                  else 'F' end as val_cve_afectado                 from                         (select cve_siniestro,cve_cobertura_tarificable,cve_cobertura_afecta, cve_causa_siniestro  as cve_causa_siniestro                         from  bddlapr.aut_siniestro_cob_afecta_271119                         where subconcepto_de_reserva = 'S' and cve_tipo_mov_siniestro = 'R')A                 left join                         (select cve_siniestro, cve_cobertura_tarificable, cve_cobertura_afecta, cve_causa_siniestro  as cve_causa_siniestro2                         from bddlapr.aut_siniestro_cob_afecta                         GROUP BY cve_siniestro, cve_cobertura_tarificable, cve_cobertura_afecta, cve_causa_siniestro, cve_causa_siniestro2)B                 on                         a.cve_siniestro  =   b.cve_siniestro and                         a.cve_cobertura_tarificable =   b.cve_cobertura_tarificable and                         a.cve_cobertura_afecta    =   b.cve_cobertura_afecta                      ) R where (cve_causa_siniestro IS NOT NULL) AND cve_causa_siniestro2 IS NOT NULL AND val_cve_afectado = 'F'

select  cve_siniestro,cve_cobertura_tarificable,cve_cobertura_afecta, fch_decretacion_pt, fch_decretacion_pt2, val_cve_afectado         from (                 Select a.cve_siniestro, a.cve_cobertura_tarificable, a.cve_cobertura_afecta, a.fch_decretacion_pt, b.fch_decretacion_pt2,                 case when a.fch_decretacion_pt = b.fch_decretacion_pt2  then 'V'                  else 'F' end as val_cve_afectado                 from                         (select cve_siniestro,cve_cobertura_tarificable,cve_cobertura_afecta, fch_decretacion_pt  as fch_decretacion_pt                         from  bddlapr.aut_siniestro_cob_afecta_271119                         where subconcepto_de_reserva = 'S' and cve_tipo_mov_siniestro = 'R')A                 left join                         (select cve_siniestro, cve_cobertura_tarificable, cve_cobertura_afecta, fch_decretacion_pt  as fch_decretacion_pt2                         from bddlapr.aut_siniestro_cob_afecta                         GROUP BY cve_siniestro, cve_cobertura_tarificable, cve_cobertura_afecta, fch_decretacion_pt, fch_decretacion_pt2)B                 on                         a.cve_siniestro  =   b.cve_siniestro and                         a.cve_cobertura_tarificable =   b.cve_cobertura_tarificable and                         a.cve_cobertura_afecta    =   b.cve_cobertura_afecta                      ) R where (fch_decretacion_pt IS NOT NULL) AND fch_decretacion_pt2 IS NOT NULL AND val_cve_afectado = 'F'

select  cve_siniestro,cve_cobertura_tarificable,cve_cobertura_afecta, fch_decretacion_pt, fch_decretacion_pt2, val_cve_afectado         from (                 Select a.cve_siniestro, a.cve_cobertura_tarificable, a.cve_cobertura_afecta, a.fch_decretacion_pt, b.fch_decretacion_pt2,                 case when a.fch_decretacion_pt = b.fch_decretacion_pt2  then 'V'                  else 'F' end as val_cve_afectado                 from                         (select cve_siniestro,cve_cobertura_tarificable,cve_cobertura_afecta, fch_decretacion_pt  as fch_decretacion_pt                         from  bddlapr.aut_siniestro_cob_afecta_271119                         where subconcepto_de_reserva = 'S' and cve_tipo_mov_siniestro = 'R')A                 left join                         (select cve_siniestro, cve_cobertura_tarificable, cve_cobertura_afecta, fch_decretacion_pt  as fch_decretacion_pt2                         from bddlapr.aut_siniestro_cob_afecta                         GROUP BY cve_siniestro, cve_cobertura_tarificable, cve_cobertura_afecta, fch_decretacion_pt, fch_decretacion_pt2)B                 on                         a.cve_siniestro  =   b.cve_siniestro and                         a.cve_cobertura_tarificable =   b.cve_cobertura_tarificable and                         a.cve_cobertura_afecta    =   b.cve_cobertura_afecta                      ) R where (fch_decretacion_pt IS NOT NULL) AND fch_decretacion_pt2 IS NOT NULL AND val_cve_afectado = 'F'

Operation Text: select  cve_siniestro,cve_cobertura_tarificable,cve_cobertura_afecta, fch_decretacion_pt, fch_decretacion_pt2, val_cve_afectado         from (                 Select a.cve_siniestro, a.cve_cobertura_tarificable, a.cve_cobertura_afecta, a.fch_decretacion_pt, b.fch_decretacion_pt2,                 case when a.fch_decretacion_pt = b.fch_decretacion_pt2  then 'V'                  else 'F' end as val_cve_afectado                 from                         (select cve_siniestro,cve_cobertura_tarificable,cve_cobertura_afecta, fch_decretacion_pt  as fch_decretacion_pt                         from  bddlapr.aut_siniestro_cob_afecta_271119                         where subconcepto_de_reserva = 'S' and cve_tipo_mov_siniestro = 'R')A                 left join                         (select cve_siniestro, cve_cobertura_tarificable, cve_cobertura_afecta, fch_decretacion_pt  as fch_decretacion_pt2                         from bddlapr.aut_siniestro_cob_afecta                         GROUP BY cve_siniestro, cve_cobertura_tarificable, cve_cobertura_afecta, fch_decretacion_pt, fch_decretacion_pt2)B                 on                         a.cve_siniestro  =   b.cve_siniestro and                         a.cve_cobertura_tarificable =   b.cve_cobertura_tarificable and                         a.cve_cobertura_afecta    =   b.cve_cobertura_afecta                      ) R where (fch_decretacion_pt IS NOT NULL) AND fch_decretacion_pt2 IS NOT NULL AND val_cve_afectado = 'V'

CREATE TABLE MES_ANT AS
SELECT anio_mes_contable, num_reclamacion, num_solicitud_tramite, id_solicitud, 
CASE WHEN num_solicitud_tramite = -999 THEN id_solicitud ELSE CAST(num_solicitud_tramite AS string) END AS tramite_siniestro,
ind_tramite_fondo_cashflow, cve_unidad_pago,
CASE 
WHEN cve_unidad_pago IN ('U002', 'U099', 'MXP')  THEN 'MXP' ELSE 'USD' END AS clasif_proveedor,
cve_modalidad, ramo, ramo_conjunto, cve_subconcepto_reserva, mto_importe_siniestral, mto_neto, 
num_poliza, num_poliza_cobranza, num_version_poliza, hosp_nom, hosp_gpo,
CASE 
WHEN hosp_nom = 'SOHIN' THEN 'Farm'
WHEN hosp_nom = 'ADM SALUD' THEN 'SAUX'
WHEN cve_subconcepto_reserva = 'HM' AND hosp_gpo = 'Grupo Star Medica' THEN 'HM' 
WHEN id_proveedor <> 0 AND hosp_tpo = 'Hosp' THEN 'Hosp'
WHEN id_proveedor <> 0 AND hosp_tpo = 'Hosp Extr' THEN 'Extranjero'
WHEN id_proveedor <> 0 AND hosp_tpo = 'Farmacias' THEN 'Extranjero'
WHEN cve_subconcepto_reserva IN ('RE','DH') AND cve_modalidad = 'RE' THEN 'RE'
WHEN id_proveedor = 0 OR hosp_tpo IN ('ND','Otro') OR hosp_tpo IS NULL AND cve_subconcepto_reserva = 'HM' THEN 'HM'
ELSE 'SAUX'
END AS TIPO_GASTO
FROM bddldes.tmp_gmm_siniestros_5
WHERE id_solicitud <> '0092051333' AND anio_mes_contable >= 201811 AND anio_mes_contable <= 201910

create table bddltrn.cnm_comisiones_asegurado_cobertura_base as
select
anio_mes_contable ,
fch_contable ,
num_poliza ,
vigencia_poliza ,
num_version_poliza ,
num_poliza_cobranza ,
num_endoso ,
contador_secuencia_objeto ,
cve_cobertura_contratada ,
des_cobertura_contratada  ,
NVL(cve_asegurado,'') AS cve_asegurado,
identificador_nvo_renovado ,
cve_cobertura_contable ,
forma_pago ,
mto_comision_prima_neta ,
mto_comision_derecho_poliza ,
mto_comision_recargo_pago_fraccionado  ,
mto_isr_comisiones  ,
mto_importe_comision_total  ,
cve_Identificador_intermediario,
des_Identificador_intermediario,
fecha_movimiento_comision  ,
cve_canal_venta_alterno  ,
porcentaje_comision  ,
segmento,
desc_segmento,
negocio,
desc_negocio,
bonos,
desc_bonos,
plan_incentivos,
pol_contr,
desc_pol_contr,
contrb,
pol_prest,
desc_pol_prest,
mot_exc,
desc_mot_exc,
cve_sistema  ,
reflect('org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils','md5Hex',
concat(
NVL( num_poliza,'') ,
NVL(cast(vigencia_poliza   as string),''),
NVL(num_endoso ,''),
NVL(cast(contador_secuencia_objeto   as string),'')
))
idmd5  ,
reflect('org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils','md5Hex',
concat(
NVL(cast(anio_mes_contable  as string),''),
fch_contable ,
NVL( num_poliza,'') ,
NVL(cast(vigencia_poliza   as string),''),
NVL(cast(num_version_poliza   as string),''),
NVL(num_poliza_cobranza ,''),
NVL(num_endoso ,''),
NVL(cast(contador_secuencia_objeto   as string),''),
NVL(cve_cobertura_contratada ,''),
NVL(des_cobertura_contratada ,''),
NVL(cve_asegurado ,''),
NVL(identificador_nvo_renovado ,''),
NVL(cve_cobertura_contable ,''),
NVL(forma_pago   ,''),
NVL(cast(mto_comision_prima_neta    as string),''),
NVL(cast(mto_comision_derecho_poliza    as string),''),
NVL(cast(mto_comision_recargo_pago_fraccionado     as string),''),
NVL(cast(mto_isr_comisiones     as string),''),
NVL(cast( mto_importe_comision_total     as string),''),
NVL(cve_Identificador_intermediario,''),
NVL(des_Identificador_intermediario,''),
fecha_movimiento_comision  ,
NVL(cve_canal_venta_alterno  ,''),
NVL(cast(porcentaje_comision    as string),''),
NVL(cve_sistema,'')
))
idmd5completo  ,
fechaaud ,
tipo_comision
from (
SELECT
distinct
anio_mes_contable ,
fch_contable ,
num_poliza ,
vigencia_poliza ,
num_version_poliza ,
num_poliza_cobranza ,
num_endoso ,
contador_secuencia_objeto ,
cve_cobertura_contratada ,
descr_cobertura_contratada     as des_cobertura_contratada,
cve_asegurado ,
identificador_nvo_renovado ,
cve_cobertura_contable ,
forma_pago ,
mto_comision_prima_neta ,
mto_comision_derecho_poliza ,
mto_comision_recargo_pago_fraccionado  ,
mto_isr_comisiones  ,
mto_importe_comision_total  ,
cve_Identificador_intermediario,
des_Identificador_intermediario,
fecha_movimiento_comision  ,
cve_canal_venta_alterno  ,
porcentaje_comision  ,
segmento,
desc_segmento,
negocio,
desc_negocio,
bonos,
desc_bonos,
plan_incentivos,
pol_contr,
desc_pol_contr,
contrb,
pol_prest,
desc_pol_prest,
mot_exc,
desc_mot_exc,
cve_sistema  ,
fechaaud ,
tipo_comision
from bddltrn.cnm_comisiones_asegurado_cobertura
where anio_mes_contable=201505 and
trim(cve_sistema) in ('CBZA','INFO') and tipo_comision='emitida'
union all
SELECT
anio_mes_contable ,
fch_contable ,
num_poliza ,

num_endoso ,
contador_secuencia_objeto ,
cve_cobertura_contratada ,

sum(mto_comision_prima_neta) mto_comision_prima_neta ,

sum(mto_isr_comisiones) mto_isr_comisiones ,
sum(mto_importe_comision_total)  mto_importe_comision_total,
cve_Identificador_intermediario,
des_Identificador_intermediario,
fecha_movimiento_comision  ,
cve_canal_venta_alterno  ,
sum(porcentaje_comision)   porcentaje_comision,
segmento,
desc_segmento,
negocio,
desc_negocio,
bonos,
desc_bonos,
plan_incentivos,
pol_contr,
desc_pol_contr,
contrb,
pol_prest,
desc_pol_prest,
mot_exc,
desc_mot_exc,
cve_sistema  ,
fechaaud ,
tipo_comision
from bddltrn.cnm_comisiones_asegurado_cobertura
where anio_mes_contable=201505 and
trim(cve_sistema) in ('CBZA','INFO') and tipo_comision='pagada'
group by

cve_asegurado ,
identificador_nvo_renovado ,
cve_cobertura_contable ,
forma_pago ,
fecha_movimiento_comision  ,
cve_canal_venta_alterno  ,
cve_Identificador_intermediario,
des_Identificador_intermediario,
cve_sistema  ,
fechaaud ,
tipo_comision
,segmento,

plan_incentivos,
pol_contr,

contrb,

mot_exc,

) C

CREATE TABLE MES_ANT AS
SELECT anio_mes_contable, num_reclamacion, num_solicitud_tramite, id_solicitud, 
CASE WHEN num_solicitud_tramite = -999 THEN id_solicitud ELSE CAST(num_solicitud_tramite AS string) END AS tramite_siniestro,
ind_tramite_fondo_cashflow, 
CASE 
WHEN cve_unidad_pago IN ('U002', 'U099', 'MXP')  THEN 'MXP' ELSE cve_unidad_pago END AS cve_unidad_pago,
cve_modalidad, ramo, ramo_conjunto, cve_subconcepto_reserva, mto_importe_siniestral, mto_neto, 
num_poliza, num_poliza_cobranza, num_version_poliza, hosp_nom, hosp_gpo,
CASE 
WHEN hosp_nom = 'SOHIN' THEN 'Farm'
WHEN hosp_nom = 'ADM SALUD' THEN 'SAUX'
WHEN cve_subconcepto_reserva = 'HM' AND hosp_gpo = 'Grupo Star Medica' THEN 'HM' 
WHEN id_proveedor <> 0 AND hosp_tpo = 'Hosp' THEN 'Hosp'
WHEN id_proveedor <> 0 AND hosp_tpo = 'Hosp Extr' THEN 'Extranjero'
WHEN id_proveedor <> 0 AND hosp_tpo = 'Farmacias' THEN 'Extranjero'
WHEN cve_subconcepto_reserva IN ('RE','DH') AND cve_modalidad = 'RE' THEN 'RE'
WHEN id_proveedor = 0 OR hosp_tpo IN ('ND','Otro') OR hosp_tpo IS NULL AND cve_subconcepto_reserva = 'HM' THEN 'HM'
ELSE 'SAUX'
END AS TIPO_GASTO
FROM bddldes.tmp_gmm_siniestros_5
WHERE id_solicitud <> '0092051333' AND anio_mes_contable >= 201811 AND anio_mes_contable <= 201910

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE bddlint.stg_gmm_cdc_alm_recibo_delta
SELECT Z.*
FROM
(
SELECT  stg.*
FROM    bddlalm.alm_recibo           actual
INNER JOIN bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo    stg ON
actual.idmd5         =   stg.idmd5
WHERE   NVL(actual.idmd5completo,'') <>  NVL(stg.idmd5completo,'')
UNION ALL
SELECT  stg.*
FROM    bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo        stg
LEFT OUTER JOIN bddlalm.alm_recibo actual ON
stg.idmd5 = actual.idmd5
WHERE   actual.idmd5 IS NULL
) Z

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE bddlint.stg_gmm_cdc_alm_recibo_con_cambios
SELECT  actual.*, CAST(from_unixtime(unix_timestamp()) AS TIMESTAMP) fechahis
FROM    bddlalm.alm_recibo        actual
INNER JOIN (SELECT idmd5, CAST(NVL(idmd5completo,'') AS VARCHAR(32)) idmd5completo FROM  bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo ) stg ON
actual.idmd5 = stg.idmd5
WHERE   actual.idmd5completo IS NOT NULL
AND actual.idmd5completo <> stg.idmd5completo

INSERT OVERWRITE DIRECTORY '/tmp/TRANS_EXECUTION_GMMAPR'
ROW FORMAT DELIMITED FIELDS TERMINATED BY '|' STORED AS TEXTFILE
SELECT TABLA_APR,WF_NAME,WORKFLOW,SUM(
CASE ESTATUS_CRU
WHEN 'PENDIENTE' THEN 1
ELSE '0'
END) as faltante
FROM bddlorg.TRANS_EXECUTION_GMMAPR
GROUP BY TABLA_APR , WF_NAME,WORKFLOW
HAVING faltante=0

INSERT OVERWRITE DIRECTORY '/tmp/TRANS_EXECUTION_GMMAPR'
ROW FORMAT DELIMITED FIELDS TERMINATED BY '|' STORED AS TEXTFILE
SELECT TABLA_APR,WF_NAME,WORKFLOW,SUM(
CASE ESTATUS_CRU
WHEN 'PENDIENTE' THEN 1
ELSE '0'
END) as faltante
FROM bddlorg.TRANS_EXECUTION_GMMAPR
GROUP BY TABLA_APR , WF_NAME,WORKFLOW
HAVING faltante=0

UPDATE bddlorg.TRANS_EXECUTION_GMMAPR
SET ESTATUS_CRU= 'FINALIZADO',
FECHA_CRU=  FROM_UNIXTIME( UNIX_TIMESTAMP(), 'dd/MM/YYYY HH:mm:ss' )
WHERE TABLA_CRU=UCASE('CNM_PRIMA_EMITIDA_POLIZA_ENDOSO')

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_F2_CNM_PRIMA_EMITIDA_POLIZA_ENDOSO_DLT AS
SELECT
CASE WHEN anio_mes_contable=0 THEN 140001 ELSE anio_mes_contable END AS anio_mes_contable,
CASE WHEN fch_contable IS NULL THEN CAST("1400-01-01 00:00:00" AS TIMESTAMP) ELSE fch_contable END AS fch_contable,
num_poliza,
vigencia_poliza,
num_version_poliza,
num_poliza_cobranza,
num_endoso,
forma_pago,
cve_tipo_endoso,
mto_prima_tecnica,
mto_recargo_descuento,
mto_prima_neta,
mto_recargo_pago_fraccionado,
pct_pago_prima,
mto_prima_neta_sin_pago_fracc,
mto_recargo_nvo_met_pago,
mto_derecho_poliza,
mto_cesion_comision,
mto_iva_poliza,
mto_prima_total,
cve_cobertura_contable,
CASE WHEN fch_emision IS NULL THEN CAST("1400-01-01 00:00:00" AS TIMESTAMP) ELSE fch_emision END AS fch_emision,
NVL(segmento, '') AS segmento,
NVL(desc_segmento, '') AS desc_segmento,
NVL(negocio, '') AS negocio,
NVL(desc_negocio, '') AS desc_negocio,
NVL(bonos, '') AS bonos,
NVL(desc_bonos, '') AS desc_bonos,
NVL(plan_incentivos, '') AS plan_incentivos,
NVL(pol_contr, '') AS pol_contr,
NVL(desc_pol_contr, '') AS desc_pol_contr,
NVL(contrb, '') AS contrb,
NVL(pol_prest, '') AS pol_prest,
NVL(desc_pol_prest, '') AS desc_pol_prest,
NVL(mot_exc, '') AS mot_exc,
NVL(desc_mot_exc, '') AS desc_mot_exc,
cve_canal_venta_alterno,
reflect('org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils','md5Hex',concat(NVL(num_poliza,''), CAST(NVL(CAST(vigencia_poliza AS INT),0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(CAST(num_version_poliza AS INT),0) AS STRING),NVL(num_poliza_cobranza,''), NVL(num_endoso,''))) AS idmd5,
reflect('org.apache.commons.codec.digest.DigestUtils','md5Hex',concat(
NVL(num_poliza,''), CAST(NVL(CAST(vigencia_poliza AS INT),0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(CAST(num_version_poliza AS INT),0) AS STRING),NVL(num_poliza_cobranza,''), NVL(num_endoso,''),
NVL(forma_pago,'') ,NVL(cve_tipo_endoso,''),CAST(NVL(CAST(mto_prima_tecnica AS INT),0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(CAST(mto_recargo_descuento AS INT),0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(CAST(mto_prima_neta AS INT),0) AS STRING),
CAST(NVL(CAST(mto_recargo_pago_fraccionado AS INT),0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(CAST(mto_cesion_comision AS INT),0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(CAST(pct_pago_prima AS INT),0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(CAST(mto_prima_neta_sin_pago_fracc AS INT),0) AS STRING),
CAST(NVL(CAST(mto_recargo_nvo_met_pago AS INT),0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(CAST(mto_derecho_poliza AS INT),0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(CAST(mto_iva_poliza AS INT),0) AS STRING),CAST(NVL(CAST(mto_prima_total AS INT),0) AS STRING),
NVL(cve_cobertura_contable,''), CAST(NVL(CAST(anio_mes_contable AS INT),0) AS STRING))) as idmd5completo,
from_unixtime(unix_timestamp()) AS FECHAAUD,
cve_sistema_int
FROM(
select * from  BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_F2_PRIMA_EMITIDA_DLT
) AS STG_POLIZA_ENDOSO_GMM_PRIMA_EMITIDA
ORDER BY fch_contable,num_poliza,num_version_poliza, cve_sistema_int

INSERT OVERWRITE TABLE bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info_medio_cobro1

INSERT  OVERWRITE   TABLE bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info_cve_banco
SELECT rec.num_recibo,
CAST(
CASE WHEN rec.tccancob = 'BC' AND rec.cve_estado_recibo = 'L'
THEN TRIM(SUBSTR(ban.CDBANCO, 2,3))
ELSE ''
END
AS VARCHAR(4))                              AS  cve_banco
FROM bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info rec
LEFT OUTER JOIN
bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info_cve_banco ban
ON      rec.num_recibo   = ban.num_recibo

INSERT  OVERWRITE   TABLE bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info_cve_banco

CREATE TABLE BDDLTRN.STG_INFO_POLIZA_ENDOSO_GMM_PRIMA_EMITIDA as
SELECT
CAST(anio_mes_contable AS INT) AS anio_mes_contable ,
CAST(CONCAT(SUBSTR(fecha_contable,1,4),"-",SUBSTR(fecha_contable,5,2),"-",SUBSTR(fecha_contable,7,2)," 00:00:00") AS timestamp) as fch_contable ,
CAST (num_poliza as varchar(14)) as num_poliza ,
CAST (indicador_vigencia as int) as vigencia_poliza,
CAST (num_version_poliza as int) as num_version_poliza  ,
CAST ('' as varchar(8)) as num_poliza_cobranza  ,
CAST ('' as varchar(6)) as num_endoso  ,
CAST (forma_pago as String) as forma_pago,
CAST ('' as varchar(3)) as cve_tipo_endoso,
CAST (SUM(mto_prima_tecnica) AS DECIMAL(20,6)) as mto_prima_tecnica,
CAST (SUM(mto_recargo_descuento) AS DECIMAL(20,6)) as mto_recargo_descuento,
CAST (SUM(mto_prima_neta)AS DECIMAL(20,6))  as mto_prima_neta,
CAST (SUM(mto_recargo_pago_fraccionado)AS DECIMAL(20,6)) as mto_recargo_pago_fraccionado,
CAST (pct_pago_prima AS DECIMAL(11,6)) as pct_pago_prima ,
CAST (SUM(mto_prima_neta_sin_pago_fracc) AS DECIMAL(20,6)) as mto_prima_neta_sin_pago_fracc,
CAST (SUM(mto_recargo_nvo_met_pago) AS DECIMAL(20,6)) as mto_recargo_nvo_met_pago,
CAST (SUM(mto_derecho_poliza) AS DECIMAL(20,6)) as mto_derecho_poliza,
CAST (SUM(mto_cesion_comision) AS DECIMAL(20,6))  as mto_cesion_comision,
CAST (SUM(mto_iva_poliza) AS DECIMAL(20,6)) as mto_iva_poliza,
CAST (SUM(mto_prima_total) AS DECIMAL(20,6)) as mto_prima_total,
CAST(SUBSTR (cve_cobertura_contable,2,3) as varchar(3)) as cve_cobertura_contable,
CAST(CONCAT(SUBSTR(fecha_emision,1,4),"-",SUBSTR(fecha_emision,5,2),"-",SUBSTR(fecha_emision,7,2)) AS timestamp) as fch_emision,
CAST(segmento AS VARCHAR(300)) AS segmento,
CAST(desc_segmento AS VARCHAR(300)) AS desc_segmento,
CAST(negocio AS VARCHAR(300)) AS negocio,
CAST(desc_negocio AS VARCHAR(300)) AS desc_negocio,
CAST(bonos AS VARCHAR(300)) AS bonos,
CAST(desc_bonos AS VARCHAR(300)) AS desc_bonos,
CAST(plan_incentivos AS VARCHAR(300)) AS plan_incentivos,
CAST(pol_contr AS VARCHAR(300)) AS pol_contr,
CAST(desc_pol_contr AS VARCHAR(300)) AS desc_pol_contr,
CAST(contrb AS VARCHAR(300)) AS contrb,
CAST(pol_prest AS VARCHAR(300)) AS pol_prest,
CAST(desc_pol_prest AS VARCHAR(300)) AS desc_pol_prest,
CAST(mot_exc AS VARCHAR(300)) AS mot_exc,
CAST(desc_mot_exc AS VARCHAR(300)) AS desc_mot_exc,
'' as cve_canal_venta_alterno,
CAST('' AS VARCHAR(32)) AS IDMD5,
CAST('' AS VARCHAR(32)) AS IDMD5COMPLETO,
CURRENT_TIMESTAMP() AS fechaaud,
CAST('INFO' AS VARCHAR(10)) AS cve_sistema_int
FROM BDDLTRN.STG_GMM_F2_IMPORTE_FILTER  as importe
group by num_poliza,
num_version_poliza,
anio_mes_contable,
cve_cobertura_contable,
segmento,
desc_segmento,
negocio,
desc_negocio,
bonos,
desc_bonos,
plan_incentivos,
pol_contr,
desc_pol_contr,
contrb,
pol_prest,
desc_pol_prest,
mot_exc,
desc_mot_exc,
indicador_vigencia,
fecha_contable,
forma_pago,
fecha_emision,
pct_pago_prima
ORDER BY  fch_contable,cve_sistema_int,num_poliza,num_version_poliza

INSERT  OVERWRITE   TABLE bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info_cve_banco1
SELECT  rec.num_recibo, m13.cdbanco, m13.tsultmod, m13.importco
FROM bddlcru.ktom13t m13
INNER JOIN
(
SELECT rec.num_recibo, numoveco, nucobpar
FROM bddlcru.ktoa13t rmc
INNER JOIN
bddlint.stg_gmm_recibo_info rec
ON  rec.num_recibo  =   trim(rmc.cdrefele)
WHERE   rmc.cdciagru            = 'SA'
AND	rmc.cdtipele            = 'RB'
AND rec.tccancob            = 'BC'
AND rec.cve_estado_recibo   = 'L'
GROUP BY rec.num_recibo, numoveco, nucobpar
) rec
ON      m13.numoveco = rec.numoveco
AND m13.nucobpar = rec.nucobpar
AND TRIM(m13.cdbanco) <> ''
GROUP BY rec.num_recibo, m13.cdbanco, m13.tsultmod, m13.importco
